{"tid":756373,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 咖喱菠蘿炒飯","createTime":"2018-07-26T03:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T03:35:49.000Z","uid":30742,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"24c57d61717c6a562b6c2d12c2d0fb2e36a47338","tid":756373,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/115534_52c4162e88ea93f8432393e7bbd3a09d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F115534_52c4162e88ea93f8432393e7bbd3a09d.jpg&h=f6dfad0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kUkrUc0yCkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkUkrUc0yCkU&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=59f3a119\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kUkrUc0yCkU</a><br />\n<br />\n屋企只要有買豬肉煲湯<br />\n舊肉一定無人吃，我又唔想嘥<br />\n所以多數都要做肉鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但無理由成日整肉鬆包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我一有肉鬆就會做呢個炒飯<br />\n又可以炒一大盤帶幾餐！真係慳唔少～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配埋個新鮮菠蘿殼，即刻好似見得人咁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我出街一定唔會叫呢個，因為萬年菠蘿殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過唔係要影相或者宴客我都好少會用個殼，因為都幾麻煩<br />\n自己食就唔攪咁多野啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <br />\n咖喱菠蘿炒飯<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/curry-pineapple-fried-rice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fcurry-pineapple-fried-rice.html&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7fdee2d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/07/curry-pineapple-fried-rice.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9019ee9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=13de14eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=Tv%2Fq8DN9P5syaUAyWEYo3LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e561a1dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"107a312c0030852a87f6b680e18dfde4692cc1ff","tid":756373,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"菠蘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30d18aabedeb33a4f34268826a93b684efab981","tid":756373,"uid":16871,